main event: Two or three lights were seen by the observer moving in a peculiar manner.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on 14 April 1961,The coordinates for the location are 1.824N 142.57E in the Far East, The lights were described as large and bright objects, The observation length was between 2-3 minutes, The military source indicated insufficient data for further classification of the phenomenon.
sighted object: two or three large, bright lights in the sky
